# Changelog

## [0.1.0-alpha] - 2025-10-25

### Added
- Complete GPU detection system (AMD, Intel, NVIDIA)
- Professional logging system with colors
- 6 GPU profiles (RDNA1/2/3/4, Intel Arc, NVIDIA RTX) - 100%
- 10 Game profiles - 100% of initial target!
  * Cyberpunk 2077
  * New World
  * Starfield
  * Red Dead Redemption 2
  * Spider-Man Remastered
  * God of War
  * Alan Wake 2
  * Hogwarts Legacy
  * The Witcher 3
  * Elden Ring
- Steam library scanner with auto-detection
- Utilities library with YAML support
- Main installer script
- Project architecture and documentation

### Status
- Core functionality: Complete ✓
- GPU profiles: 6/6 Complete ✓
- Game profiles: 10/10 Complete ✓
- Steam scanner: Complete ✓
- Installation: Manual (full automation in progress)
- Documentation: In progress
